      <h2>Mission Statement</h2>
      <p>KIT Federal Credit Union is a Member-Owned Financial Institution
        whose purpose is to provide a full range of financial services, of
        the highest quality, offered in a personal and professional manner,
        consistent with the Credit Union's long-term financial stability.</p>
       
